        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking / Hydroisomerization reaction",
        "description": "使用三种不同的金属（镍、钴、钼）负载在SAPO-11上的催化剂，以正十六烷(n-hexadecane)为模型原料进行活性测试，评估其转化率。镍基催化剂显示出最高的转化率（70%）。",
        "text_snippet": "First, three metals, nickel, cobalt, and molybdenum, were selected to be loaded on SAPO-11 separately and their activities were tested over the model feedstock, n-hexadecane. Among the three catalysts, nickel SAPO-11 shows the highest conversion of 70%.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      },
      {
        "experiment_id": 2,
        "reaction_type": "加氢裂化/加氢异构化反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrocracking / Hydroisomerization reaction",
        "description": "使用优化的Ni/SAPO-11(CA)催化剂，以棕榈油衍生的加氢烷烃(HA)为原料，在优化条件下（温度380°C，压力52 bar，LHSV 0.5 h⁻¹，H₂/原料比1250）生产加氢可再生航空燃料(HRJ)，获得了73%的转化率和6.1的异构烷烃与正构烷烃比(I-to-N)。",
        "text_snippet": "Through the Taguchi method, the optimal operating conditions were found to be: temperature of 380°C, pressure of 52 bar, liquid hourly space velocity of 0.5 h⁻¹, and H₂-to-feedstock ratio of 1250, which yielded in 73% conversion to HRJ with 6.1 isomer-to-normal (I-to-N) alkane ratio.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
